{"attributes":{"title":"Error events by type","description":"Count of error/failure events over time, broken down by event_type (top 10), using a self-adapting wildcard query -- event_type:*error* or event_type:*failed*, excluding error_monitor_* (the error-scanner's own housekeeping events, not actual failures). FIXES a staleness bug: the prior committed panel hardcoded 3 event types (elasticsearch_index_failed, model_call_error, entity_extraction_failed), and 2 of those 3 went dead 24-55 days ago (model_call_error last emitted 2026-06-07; entity_extraction_failed last emitted 2026-05-07) -- so the panel visually showed errors declining toward zero, which was actually just instrumentation churn, not improving health. Verified live over the last 7 days: 381 real error/failure events, dominated by elasticsearch_index_failed (170), generic error (107, level=ERROR asyncio/connector cleanup warnings), and slm_health_probe_http_error (90). This wildcard query self-adapts to future event-type churn instead of silently going stale again.","visualizationType":"lnsXY","state":{"visualization":{"legend":{"isVisible":true,"position":"right"},"valueLabels":"hide","fittingFunction":"Linear","axisTitlesVisibilitySettings":{"x":true,"yLeft":true,"yRight":true},"tickLabelsVisibilitySettings":{"x":true,"yLeft":true,"yRight":true},"labelsOrientation":{"x":0,"yLeft":0,"yRight":0},"gridlinesVisibilitySettings":{"x":true,"yLeft":true,"yRight":true},"preferredSeriesType":"bar_stacked","layers":[{"layerId":"908039c5-37b9-4832-b94d-e986aeac3eae","accessors":["36314f27-9a08-4d61-bdbf-d79571e7c241"],"position":"top","seriesType":"bar_stacked","showGridlines":false,"layerType":"data","colorMapping":{"assignments":[],"specialAssignments":[{"rules":[{"type":"other"}],"color":{"type":"loop"},"touched":false}],"paletteId":"default","colorMode":{"type":"categorical"}},"xAccessor":"7e58f4ea-2bfb-4cbd-afbe-cb664d52bfbd","splitAccessor":"adb1d124-ce06-4ba3-87d9-f7d3e208fe42"}]},"query":{"query":"(eve